{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"siteUrl":"http://docs.inspireui.com","title":"InspireUI Document","description":"InspireUI document"}},"markdownRemark":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Customization","date":null,"date_pretty":null,"path":null,"meta_title":"BeoNews Pro - React Native mobile app for Wordpress","meta_description":"BeoNews is an app that does magic for your website by converting your Wordpress website into mobile true native app with customized contents within a fillip.","image":null,"next":null,"sidebar":"beonews","toc":null,"keywords":["beonews","beonews pro magento","wordpress app","react-native","react-native app"]},"html":"<p>This section will guide how to change the app logo, icons, splash screens</p>\n<h2 id=\"change-the-default-home-layout\"><a href=\"#change-the-default-home-layout\" aria-label=\"change the default home layout permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Change the default Home layout</h2>\n<p>It's possible to customize the app homepage screen to show the default layout as your wish, open <code class=\"language-text\">App/common/config.js</code>and edit the <strong>homeLayout</strong> option to one of these values:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Constants.Layout.mansory</li>\n<li>Constants.Layout.horizontal</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\">  <span class=\"token comment\">// The default value is horizontal</span>\n  homeLayout<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> Constants<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>Layout<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>horizontal</code></pre></div>\n<p>It's possible to customize the homepage by edit App/Container/Home/index.js and change the layout type (2 column, 3 column...) by only return the PostList component</p>\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/1d7304623b2d172aace32751725ddccd/8c14d/beonew-1.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 800px;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 42.41071428571429%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"beonew 1\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/1d7304623b2d172aace32751725ddccd/efcfb/beonew-1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/1d7304623b2d172aace32751725ddccd/11053/beonew-1.png 200w,\n/static/1d7304623b2d172aace32751725ddccd/1b42c/beonew-1.png 400w,\n/static/1d7304623b2d172aace32751725ddccd/efcfb/beonew-1.png 800w,\n/static/1d7304623b2d172aace32751725ddccd/d25cb/beonew-1.png 1200w,\n/static/1d7304623b2d172aace32751725ddccd/22e61/beonew-1.png 1600w,\n/static/1d7304623b2d172aace32751725ddccd/8c14d/beonew-1.png 2240w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<h2 id=\"change-the-homepage-horizontal-layout\"><a href=\"#change-the-homepage-horizontal-layout\" aria-label=\"change the homepage horizontal layout permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Change the HomePage horizontal layout</h2>\n<p>Open App/common/AppConfig.json then you can change the horizontal layout with flexible config by update the option <strong>HorizonLayout:</strong></p>\n<blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Tags</strong>: the tag ids from Wordpress blog, it could be set as array [x, x...] </li>\n<li><strong>Categories</strong>: the category ids, , it could be set as array [x, x...] </li>\n<li><strong>row</strong>: the number of row support on the list, default is one row </li>\n<li><strong>paging</strong>: blog per page from swiping, default is false </li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>layout</strong>: support 8 kind of layouts: </p>\n<ul>\n<li>banner,</li>\n<li>twoColumn</li>\n<li>threeColumn</li>\n<li>threeColumnHigh</li>\n<li>list</li>\n<li>listRight</li>\n<li>card</li>\n<li>flexColumn: is flexible column layout that you can config both width &#x26; height</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"example-showing-the-content-as-banner-view\"><a href=\"#example-showing-the-content-as-banner-view\" aria-label=\"example showing the content as banner view permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Example: showing the content as Banner View</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token string\">`tags: [39], paging: true, layout: Constants.Layout.banner`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>This mean show all recent post which have tag <strong>id:39</strong>, show as the per page with sticky support via <strong>paging:true</strong>, this is show as the <strong>Layout.banner</strong> </p>\n<h3 id=\"example-showing-the-content-as-2-column-view\"><a href=\"#example-showing-the-content-as-2-column-view\" aria-label=\"example showing the content as 2 column view permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Example: showing the content as 2 column view</h3>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">{</code>name: 'Top Videos', categories: [34], layout: Constants.Layout.twoColumn}</p>\n<p>Show the category <strong>id:21</strong> with label 'feature products'</p>\n<p>The horizon layout is show as three two by support Constants.Layout.twoColumn</p>\n<h2 id=\"customize-the-components-color\"><a href=\"#customize-the-components-color\" aria-label=\"customize the components color permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Customize the Components Color</h2>\n<p>Open <code class=\"language-text\">/App/Common/Color.js</code> file in project.</p>\n<p>You could change most of components color in Color section.</p>\n<p>For example, you could change the color of Tabbar to any color you like, then reload the app to see the effect.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token operator\">...</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">//Product tabs</span>\ntabbar<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'rgba(255, 255, 255, 1)'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\ntabbarTint<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"#1CB5B4\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\ntabbarColor<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"#D5D8DE\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\ntabActiveText<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'#fff'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">...</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"change-the-logo-and-icons\"><a href=\"#change-the-logo-and-icons\" aria-label=\"change the logo and icons permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Change the logo and Icons</h2>\n<p>Open <code class=\"language-text\">App/common/images.js</code>to map your news image Logo and icon file.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\">  logo<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">require</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"@images/logo.png\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  logoSpin<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">require</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"@images/logoSpin.png\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>You can able to change other icons from the navigation such as home, layout, search, logout...</p>\n<h2 id=\"change-the-splash-screen\"><a href=\"#change-the-splash-screen\" aria-label=\"change the splash screen permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Change the splash screen</h2>\n<p>To change splash screen on Expo version try to edit the <a href=\"https://docs.expo.io/versions/latest/guides/splash-screens#__next\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">app.json</a></p>\n<p>To change splash screen on Pro version, you can refer to <a href=\"https://medium.com/the-react-native-log/change-default-launch-screen-in-react-native-ios-app-544f94f1e947\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">this guide</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"change-the-category-images\"><a href=\"#change-the-category-images\" aria-label=\"change the category images permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Change the category images</h2>\n<p>Open common/config.js file and edit the step3 section:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\">imageCategories<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    drink<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">require</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"@images/category/cate1.jpg\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    chicken<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">require</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"@images/category/cate2.jpg\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>The key should mapping with your category <strong>slug</strong> category name, the slug name could pick from the Wordpress dashboard admin</p>","fields":{"slug":"/beonews/customization/"},"timeToRead":3,"excerpt":"This section will guide how to change the app logo, icons, splash screens Change the default Home layout It's possible to customize the app…","fileAbsolutePath":"/Users/minh/Data/Projects/documents/inspireui-documents/docs/content/beonews/customization.md"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/beonews/customization/"}}